    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts reliably, making it an excellent choice for a daily driver. While the exterior shows some light surface scratches and the interior has minor wear on the driver's seat, all electronics and safety features are fully functional. This is a dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
